    "body": "## Report incorrect documentation\r\n\r\n**Location of incorrect documentation**\r\nhttps://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/20812f2f7bd194c7be9bc75753b6176e87f8768c/CONTRIBUTING.md?plain=1#L118-L137\r\n\r\n\r\n**Describe the problems or issues found in the documentation**\r\n\r\nJDK9+ build doc is stale. \r\n\r\nConventional jar creation is a useful feature in and of itself for simplified single-shim jar deployment. However, it is no longer a requirement for JDK9+ runtime since we no longer need to force-update the parent AppClassLoader\r\n\r\nScala Maven Plugin should be upgraded for the entire build should  not require an override\r\n\r\n**Steps taken to verify documentation is incorrect**\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n**Suggested fix for documentation**\r\n\r\n```[tasklist]\r\n### Tasks\r\n- [x] Fix #5576\r\n- [ ] Stop documenting an override of the scala-maven-plugin-version\r\n- [x] Create a separate section explaining `-DallowConventionalDistJar=true`\r\n```",
